description:
FOX Sports and NFL Network analyst Bucky Brooks joins Colin to examine the Aaron Rodgers-Green Bay Packers standoff, the Dallas Cowboys on Hard Knocks (again) and more. Finally, Colin closes with his ten sports figures who will shape the industry in "Best For Last."
